{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_CFlameMissile}}
'''A_CFlameMissile'''

(no parameters)

Removes the {{Flag|INVISIBLE}} flag and plays the sound ClericFlameExplode on the BODY channel.  In addition it spawns 8 {{Class|CircleFlame}} actors at 90 degree angles in a circle around the actor in which it hit.  These actors are set such that they begin rotating (4 in one direction, 4 in the other) around the actor.

This code pointer is restricted to {{Class|CFlameMissile}} and actors inheriting from it.

